sentences: Susanne Alfvengren (born Susanne Irene Lund, 12 February 1959 in Visby, Gotland, Sweden) is a Swedish singer.
In 1984, Susanne Alfvengren had a hit with När vi rör varann.
She competed in Melodifestivalen 2009 with the song "Du är älskad där du går", which was knocked out from the contest after the semi-final.
In 1986–1987, she scored a vocal duet hit with Mikael Rickfors, with "Som stormen river öppet hav".
